# astrion-skill v1
goal: Start a timer from a natural-language duration
trigger:
  - phrase: "timer"
  - phrase: "set a timer"
  - phrase: "start timer"
do: |
  Parse the user's text after the trigger for a duration (e.g., "10
  minutes", "1 hour", "25 min"). Default to 10 minutes if no duration
  parseable. Launch the Timer app pre-seeded with that duration and
  auto-started. Show a notification confirming the timer started.
constraints:
  level: L2
  budget_tokens: 200
  reversibility: FREE
